11:| `default` | Claude `sessionKey` value | `AppModel.validateAndSaveSessionKey(_:)` after local + remote validation | `AppModel.loadSessionKey()`, `UsageService` through Keychain during refresh | `AppModel.clearSessionKey()` | `KeychainRepository.serviceName = "com.claudemeter.sessionkey"`; generic password; `kSecAttrAccessibleAfterFirstUnlock`; `kSecAttrSynchronizable = false` | Service name intentionally retained from ClaudeMeter for continuity. `AppSettings.cachedOrganizationId` stores org UUID separately in UserDefaults. |
