16:- `Pinemeter/Repositories/KeychainRepository.swift`: `com.claudemeter.sessionkey` remains the Keychain service name.
27:  - `Pinemeter/Views/Setup/SetupWizardView.swift` first-launch setup accepts a Claude session key or Cookie header containing `sessionKey`.
30:  - `Pinemeter/Services/SessionKeyImportService.swift` queries local browser cookies for domain suffix `claude.ai` and cookie name `sessionKey` using SweetCookieKit.
36:- `AppModel.validateAndSaveSessionKey(_:)` constructs `SessionKey`, calls `usageService.validateSessionKey(sessionKey)`, then fetches organizations with `usageService.fetchOrganizations(sessionKey:)`.
41:- Stored only through `KeychainRepository.save(sessionKey:account: "default")`.
46:- `UsageService` retrieves the default account from Keychain and calls `NetworkService`.
47:- `NetworkService.request(... sessionKey:)` sends `Cookie: sessionKey=<value>` to `https://claude.ai/api`.
51:- `SettingsView.loadSettings()` loads the full saved Claude session key into local SwiftUI state `sessionKey` so it can be edited/saved again. Even if rendered through a secure field, this is a display/local-state exposure surface.
57:- `AppModel.clearSessionKey()` deletes account `default`, clears cached organization ID, resets setup state, clears usage/error state, and cancels refresh task.
58:- Recovery/error paths include `SessionKeyError`, `SessionKeyImportError`, `AppError.noSessionKey`, `AppError.sessionKeyInvalid`, `AppError.organizationNotFound`, and provider/network errors.
65:  - `__Secure-next-auth.session-token.0`,
66:  - optional `__Secure-next-auth.session-token.1`,
67:  - full Cookie header,
77:- Stored through `KeychainRepository.save(sessionKey: trimmedCookie, account: "chatgpt")`.
78:- The stored value may be a raw token, full Cookie header, or split-cookie-derived string depending on input path.
82:- `AppModel.refreshChatGPTUsage()` retrieves account `chatgpt` from Keychain.
83:- `ChatGPTUsageService.cookieHeader(from:)` builds a Cookie header.
93:- `AppModel.clearChatGPTSessionCookie()` deletes account `chatgpt`, clears `hasChatGPTSessionCookie`, usage data, and error message.
94:- `SettingsView.clearChatGPTSessionCookie()` clears local token/header state and validation message.
